                或 <xref href="https://api.flutter.dev/objcdoc/Protocols/FlutterTexture.html" format="html" scope="external">FlutterTexture</xref>。</li>
                <li>iOS/macOS/Windows: <xref href="https://api.flutter.dev/objcdoc/Protocols/FlutterTexture.html" format="html" scope="external">FlutterTexture</xref>。</li>
                <li>该类不适用于 Web 平台。</li>
            </ul></p>
